# Short Prompt Mapping

Map user intent to first-class commands directly.

Examples:
- "List pages" -> `pages.list`
- "Show widgets on login" -> `widgets.list {nameOrId:"login"}`
- "Get this widget" -> `widget.get {nameOrId:<page>, nodeId:<id>}`
- "Change brand.ai to James NoCode on login" -> locate text node then `widget.set`
- "Create a button under this container" -> `widget.create`
- "Remove widget id-Button_x on onboarding" -> `widget.delete`
- "Rename Onboarding to Intro" -> `page.update`

Always return resolved IDs and fileKeys in response summaries.
